Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.75,0:01:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.73,0:01:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜和我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你而言 谁比较重要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你变了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想改变的 只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.24,0:02:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果对战斗抱有疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个牺牲的就是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘了羽佐间和甲洋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.51,0:02:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这话…是认真的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.01,0:02:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有能代替这只左眼的东西
